                FLIR Systems PathFindIR - Driving Thermal Imager Camera Systems — 6 products / 9 models
 — Page 1










FLIR PathFindIR is a revolutionary solution to night time driving. Your car can easily outrun your headlights, making them ineffective at giving you enough warning time to stop or react to an animal, a pedestrian, cyclist, or a broken down car. The FLIR thermal imaging technology doesn't read light, like night vision cameras - it read the heat emitted by objects. Cooler objects such as cars, trees, and building are dark. Warmer objects like people and animals are bright. This allows you to peer through the dark in fog or smoke and react to potential hazards before they can a dangerous situation. FLIR PathFindIR Thermal Imager can be easily mounted behind the car radiator grill and connected to the in-car monitor.At OpticsPlanet, we are proud of our great line of FLIR PathFindIR products, and we back it by offering FREE SHIPPING on orders over $49. We also make shopping easy by having product experts standing by to answer any questions you may have, and offering great How-To Guides and Blog Posts for information at your fingertips! Drive with more confidence with the FLIR PathFindIR Series.














