                FLIR H-Series Thermal Imaging Cameras - FLIR Handheld Thermal Imager Devices — 10 products / 21 models
 — Page 1










FLIR Systems H-Series thermal devices provide law enforcement officers with the tools they need to make split second decisions that could mean life or death. These incredible thermal imaging devices from the thermal experts at FLIR allow officers to see suspects in total darkness, through smoke, dust, fog, foliage, and camouflage, improving and maximizing the effectiveness of the mission, capabilities of the operation, and the officer's safety. With the FLIR proprietary digital detail enhancement and a 320x240 resolution, your thermal images will be clear and crisp, whether you're viewing the white hot or black hot color palettes. When you need a tactical advantage, FLIR night vision and thermal imagers are the best value, in darkness or in light, in good weather and bad.OpticsPlanet strives for your satisfaction, so we offer FREE 2 DAY SHIPPING on all orders over $49, a wealth of information available in our How-To Articles and Blog Posts, and our product experts are standing by to answer any questions you might have by phone, email, and chat! Shop FLIR H-Series Thermal Imager Devices today!














