REVIEWS






FLIR ONE for iOS
Thermal Mobile Accessory





Good device at this price point


I have had my FLIR One for over 6 months now - and I really like it. I have used my camera to check for heat leaks in my house insulation - to check my in-floor electric heat for hot spots - to check for critters in my attic - and to look at my electrical panels to see if I had any hot breakers. I have even used it to check to make sure a carpet wasn't wet after an accident during a dinner party.
 






FLIR C2
Pocket-Sized Infrared Camera





Exactly what I needed!


The C2 with its MSX technology is just perfect for my needs as a home inspector. It's reasonably priced. It's compact and easy to use. I can carry it with me at all times during my inspections.














