At Home
Do a pre-purchase thermal home inspection and find those hidden problems that can cost you thousands.  Optimize your home’s energy efficiency.  Spot overloaded circuits to improve your home’s safety.  Want to see like a professional - upgrade to the FLIR ONE Pro.
See more 


At Work
Home professionals can use the FLIR ONE Pro to find water leaks in roofs, HVAC issues or electrical problems around the jobsite.  Take the FLIR ONE Pro to the garage to inspect automobiles for parasitic draw on the electrical systems and heating and cooling troubleshooting.
See More 


At Play
Observe wildlife and navigate trails in complete darkness. Have more restful nights by checking your campsite for animals. Have more fun putting a spin on a night game of hide-and-go-seek.
See More 









