For Your Life
FLIR thermal imaging can enhance any busy lifestyle. Whether you’re exploring the great outdoors, enjoying a night on the town, or tackling projects around the house, FLIR thermal vision will reveal an unseen world that will amaze you.


 
 
 
 
Recreational Boating
We make navigation stress free and simple - see at night with FLIR thermal night vision, catch more fish, and cruise even further with Raymarine marine electronics.
EXPLORE FLIR MARINE PRODUCTS
 

 
 
 
 

 
Meet The FLIR Fishing Team
Jim Kelly, Captain of the FLIR Fishing Team explains how FLIR Cameras give the team a competitive advantage for speed and safety on the water
Watch the video



See the day in a minute.
RapidRecap™ is an exclusive technology that simultaneously presents video eventsrecorded at different points in a chosen timeframe to help users quickly review videofootage that could span hours.
EXPLORE
 

 
 
 
 
Personal Night Vision
Our personal thermal cameras let you discover a world hidden by darkness.  Experience wildlife at night like you never have before.
EXPLORE
 

 
 
 
 

 
A Perfect Tool for Finding Wildlife
Tools for detecting wildlife have evolved a lot in the last century. Binoculars are now commonly used throughout the world, followed by light amplifying nighttime vision systems that can be used to spot animals at night. Now there's a new wildlife detection tool on the market: the FLIR Scout Series handheld thermal imaging camera.
Read the full story  



Thermal for Smartphones
Revolutionize the way you see your world with the FLIR ONE© thermal camera attachment for iPhone or Android. FLIR ONE translates thermal energy into dynamic color images for personal safety, home repairs, outdoor adventures, and even artistic expression.
EXPLORE
 



Driver Vision Enhancement
PathFindIR™ II is a powerful thermal night vision camera that lets you see clearly in total darkness, regardless of the vehicle you’re driving or the road you’re on.
EXPLORE
 



 
 






 











